name: Kreme
description:
Kreme Tee.

We have created the perfect joint. A piece a couple of dough makers like Ben & Jerry would be proud of, sweeten up that baking process. 

Size's (Inches)
Small: 34 - 36
Medium: 38 - 40
Large: 42 - 44

100% soft cotton. Crew neck taped neck and shoulders, seamless double-needle collar sleeves and bottom hems.
We recommend washing at 30 degrees inside out and hang dry.

name: Kreme x Five
description:
Kreme 5 Panel Cap.

Our first custom 5 panel, featuring our 'Dope Kreme' design patterned all over. A piece as unique as they get, limited edition and each with a slightly different placed pattern making no two the same. 

Black suede peak.

Sewn on front leather patch with logo.

Adjustable strap on back.
